{"tid":1930821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"愛斯賓奴官方宣佈隊內6人感染新冠 尚未公佈名單","createTime":"2020-03-17T22:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T04:11:54.000Z","uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7b26556efdc263711cb1a956b8d7437245971817","tid":1930821,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:18:10.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月18日消息，愛斯賓奴通過官方網站宣佈，一線隊球員以及工作人員中共有6人感染新型冠狀病毒，但還沒有公佈具體的名單。<br />\n<br />\n  愛斯賓奴在公告中表示，球會組織了第一批球員和工作人員的檢查，發現有6人新冠病毒的檢查結果為陽性。這6人都有輕微症狀。<br />\n<br />\n  據西班牙廣播電視台17日報導，過去24小時內，西班牙新冠肺炎確診病例增至11178例，新增1987例，死亡491例。"},{"pid":"d872fa4f6ceaf33146a8578c0d8063900b580157","tid":1930821,"uid":17042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:22:33.000Z","msg":"冇女"},{"pid":"a7748735096e98c3db0fa74e006fd32ef2a340e2","tid":1930821,"uid":27416,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:26:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n其實係咪職業球隊有錢驗先show 到咁多人中"},{"pid":"7bc38cbbf8cd040d0cb3b6ed61c87895dbae963c","tid":1930821,"uid":308251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:29:47.000Z","msg":"西班牙同義大利都咁大鑊，代表咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5879f2f6efc25d6ce658b4e28e4edff174645b7e","tid":1930821,"uid":143289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d872fa4f6ceaf33146a8578c0d8063900b580157","tid":1930821,"uid":17042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:22:33.000Z","msg":"冇女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:30:15.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"8c8bf0ba5e43f958ebec41b697a020513c9e4c95","tid":1930821,"uid":191804,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:33:06.000Z","msg":"應該係武磊傳染比隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1c9a787d05db98df524583e56b32cd35f671e1","tid":1930821,"