n  不過中國球迷最關心的還是武磊，目前沒有武磊檢測結果的消息。包括武磊本人也沒有透露任何的信息。<br />\n<br />\n  在社交網站上，很多球迷都在關注武磊的情況。<br />\n<br />\n  有球迷發問：「愛斯賓奴6人確診，究竟有沒有武磊？」更多的球迷是祝福：「希望武磊中招！」「武磊是中國足球的希望，希望他確診。」（沙治奧）"},{"pid":"842dab266ff122321b2fbf1520a6ec1b8f7ed9e0","tid":1930821,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:51:42.000Z","msg":"比無女傳染"},{"pid":"ba7ab0b254d3cf56110f532cd8238cb690e8e5b6","tid":1930821,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1514ab030da260a58fb7bf7dcafae3d06423c8ac","tid":1930821,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7748735096e98c3db0fa74e006fd32ef2a340e2","tid":1930821,"uid":27416,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:26:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n其實係咪職業球隊有錢驗先show 到咁多人中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:24:41.000Z","msg":"出名先報道啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:53:46.000Z","msg":"如果輕病抖幾日無事，就變左有抗體"},{"pid":"168d1076fd17a0bbf1849cfc9508bb2e1b54d58e","tid":1930821,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f678be5ed0a2b4dcdf006ff82527d02671b1ba4b","tid":1930821,"uid":266051,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T23:07:48.000Z","msg":"巴打，雖然知你係抄番嚟，但麻煩你出之前幫手改正，係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong>啊<br />\n<br />\nbtw，係咪有某個24號份？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬係支那人<br />\n點會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31c3c187f765db7df51b1e21fbce569df0ea40d","tid":1930821,"uid":235174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1009619afd72fef8a942799aa2d1aac7fc42d5f","tid":1930821,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c8bf0ba5e43f958ebec41b697a020513c9e4c95","tid":1930821,"uid":191804,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:33:06.000Z","msg":"應該係武磊傳染比隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f